These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, journalist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, subway
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the photographer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | reading       | drawing |
| Job         | journalist | photographer  |
| Sport       | sailing    | weightlifting    |
| Transport   | subway       | motorbike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, animation
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, badminton
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the coach is on the far left##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | juice |
| Job           | coach | security-guard      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | western      |
| Sport         | basketball | badminton     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
There 2 different types of food: cherry, corn
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, funk
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, motorbike
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | 7up | coffee  |
| Food          | cherry    | corn   |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | hip-hop   |
| Transport     | motorbike     | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, zucchini
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, photographer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, gospel
1. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
2. the designer is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk       | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | zucchini         | asparagus    |
| Job           | photographer | designer    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic           | gospel   |

