2 different pets are kept: snake, pony
1. the canadian is the owner of the pony##1
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | papaya | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | techno      |
| Nationality   | mexican | canadian    |
| Pet           | snake    | pony    |

