The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, adventure
2 different pets are kept: turtle, horse
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike
1. the architect is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the architect is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the owner of the turtle is the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | software-developer | architect     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy          | adventure |
| Pet           | turtle          | horse    |
| Transport     | trike            | quad-bike       |

 